u récapitulatif des caractéristiques typiques de ces revêtements.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aPipingxCorrosion. 0aSurface coating. 4aMaterials. 7aTechnology & Engineering / Materials Science / General.2bisacsh1 aBouchardy, Murielle, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aBrolon, Thierry, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aCefracor, , eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEDP Sciences Contemporary eBook-Package 2016-2020z978311075640140uhttps://doi.org/10.1051/978-2-7598-1991-140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782759819911423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9782759819911/original  a978-3-11-075640-1  EDP Sciences Contemporary eBook-Package 2016-2020c2016d2020  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_CHCOMSGSEN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK